org.multigraph
Class DatetimeValue

java.lang.Object
  org.multigraph.DataValue
      org.multigraph.DatetimeValue

public class DatetimeValue
extends DataValue

DatetimeValue is the DataValue implementation for the DATETIME data type (DataValue.Type.DATETIME). It represents a moment in time, in the UTC (GMT) time zone, with milliscond precision. The value is stored internally as a double that represents the number of milliseconds since the epoch (i.e., the Unix timestamp value, but stored as a double rather than an integer).
